  <h2>✨ About SoulSpeak</h2>
  <p><strong>SoulSpeak</strong> is a safe and creative space where emotions find their voice.</p>

  <p>Whether it’s through a <em>poem</em>, a heartfelt <em>story</em>, a touching <em>shayri</em>, or a deep <em>reflection</em>, SoulSpeak welcomes you to express what words often leave behind.</p>

  <p>This platform is for those who write to <strong>heal</strong>, to <strong>connect</strong>, and to <strong>share</strong> their unspoken truths.</p>

  <p>Every piece shared here is a window into someone's soul — <em>raw</em>, <em>real</em>, and <em>resonant</em>.</p>

  <p><strong>Speak your heart.</strong><br>
     <strong>Let your words echo.</strong><br>
     <strong>This is your space — your SoulSpeak.</strong>
  </p>
